  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK566">
<l>kaṭuñcollaṉ kaṇṇila ṉāyi ṉeṭumcelva </l>
<l> nīṭiṉṟi yāṅkē keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The abundant wealth of the king whose words are harsh and whose looks are void of kindness, will instantly perish instead of abiding long, with him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
